Symbol.Script_UI:
! ============================================================================= ! Localization ! =============================================================================
! iMoldingObject MOLDING_STRAIGHT = 1 MOLDING_CURVED_POS = 2 MOLDING_CURVED_NEG = 3
! iClosingSide CLOSING_SIDE1 = 1 CLOSING_SIDE2 = 2 CLOSING_SIDE_BOTH = 3
dim idxUIControl[] for i = 1 to vardim1(stMoldingStyle) idxUIControl[i] = i next i
! ============================================================================= ! Tabpage Structure Definition ! =============================================================================
TABID_ROOT = -1 _idxTab = 1 TABID_STYLE = _idxTab : _idxTab = _idxTab + 1 TABID_GEOMETRY = _idxTab : _idxTab = _idxTab + 1 TABID_REPRES = _idxTab : _idxTab = _idxTab + 1 TABID_DESCRIPTIONS = _idxTab : _idxTab = _idxTab + 1
! ============================================================================= ! Display actual tabpages ! =============================================================================
ui_dialog `Параметры Профиля` ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
ui_page TABID_STYLE, TABID_ROOT , `Стиль`, "uiTab_Style_flat(1)" gosub "stylePage"
ui_page TABID_GEOMETRY, TABID_ROOT , `Размеры`, "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" gosub "geometryPage"
ui_page TABID_REPRES, TABID_ROOT, `Отображение и Покрытия`, "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" gosub "AppearancePage"
ui_page TABID_DESCRIPTIONS, TABID_ROOT, `Описание`, "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)" gosub "descriptionPage"
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Image links for archive ! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- file_dependence "uiTab_Style_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
! ============================================================================= end ! =============================================================================
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Subroutines ! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- "stylePage": ! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
x1 = 0 xEnd = 444 yEnd = 265 pageStartY = 0 yCurrent = pageStartY
if vardim1(stMoldingStyle) > 0 then ui_infield{4} "iMoldingStyle", x1, yCurrent, xEnd - x1, yEnd - yCurrent, 1,"ui_moldingtypes(14)", 18, 5, 105, 125, 90, 90, idxUIControl, stMoldingStyle, idxUIControl endif
return
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- "geometryPage": ! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- x1 = 0 x2 = 170 _infHeight = 19 _yCurr = pageStartY _dy = 24
if iMoldingObject = 1 then ui_infield{3} "bClosingEnds", x1, _yCurr, x2 - 2, _infHeight, 7, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `Профилированный Торец`, 0, "", `Профилированный Торец`, 1
ui_infield{3} "iClosingSide", x2, _yCurr, 97, _infHeight, 8, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", stClosingSide[1], 1, "", stClosingSide[2], 2, "", stClosingSide[3], 3 _yCurr = _yCurr + _dy ui_separator x1, _yCurr, xEnd, _yCurr endif
xPict = 9 yPict = 116 PictWidth = 40 PictHeight = 40
if iMoldingStyle < 7 then ui_pict 1, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_Moldings_Profile1.png else if iMoldingStyle > 6 and iMoldingStyle < 13 then ui_pict 2, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_Moldings_Profile2.png else ui_pict 3, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_Moldings_Profile3.png endif endif
_yCurr = yPict - _infHeight - 3 ui_infield "profileWidth", xPict - 3, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Ширина Профиля`
_yCurr = yPict + 16 ui_infield "profileHeight", xPict + PictWidth + 3, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Высота Профиля`
xPict = 228 PictWidth = 148
if iMoldingObject = 1 then ! Straight
_yCurr = yPict + 16 if not(bClosingEnds) then ui_pict 4, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_StraightMolding_Dim1.png ui_infield "alpha", xPict + PictWidth + 3, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Угол Подрезки Справа` ui_infield "beta", xPict - 63, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Угол Подрезки Слева` else if iClosingSide = CLOSING_SIDE1 then ui_pict 5, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_StraightMolding_Dim2.png ui_infield "alpha", xPict + PictWidth + 3, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Угол Подрезки Справа` else if iClosingSide = CLOSING_SIDE2 then ui_pict 6, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_StraightMolding_Dim3.png ui_infield "beta", xPict - 63, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Угол Подрезки Слева` else ui_pict 7, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_StraightMolding_Dim4.png endif endif endif
_yCurr = yPict - _infHeight - 3 ui_infield "A", xPict + 29, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Размер 1` else yPict = 79 PictHeight = 115
if iMoldingObject = 3 then ! Curved 01 ui_pict 8, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_Curved01Molding_Dim.png else ! Curved 02 ui_pict 9, xPict, yPict, PictWidth, PictHeight, 1 ! ui_Curved02Molding_Dim.png endif
_yCurr = yPict - _infHeight - 3 ui_infield "beta", xPict + 96, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Угол Подрезки Слева`
_yCurr = yPict + 86 ui_infield "malpha", xPict - 63, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Угол Профиля` ui_infield "alpha", xPict + PictWidth + 3, _yCurr, 60, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Угол Подрезки Справа`
_yCurr = yPict + PictHeight + 3 ui_infield "rr", xPict + 28, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Радиус Профиля` endif return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "AppearancePage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
dim st2DParamNames[5][2] st2DParamNames[1][1] = "gs_line_type" : st2DParamNames[1][2] = "ui_list_contLineType_flat(1)" st2DParamNames[2][1] = "gs_cont_pen" : st2DParamNames[2][2] = "ui_list_contourPen_flat(1)" st2DParamNames[3][1] = "gs_fill_type" : st2DParamNames[3][2] = "ui_list_fillType_flat(1)" st2DParamNames[4][1] = "gs_fill_pen" : st2DParamNames[4][2] = "ui_list_fillPen_flat(1)" st2DParamNames[5][1] = "gs_back_pen" : st2DParamNames[5][2] = "ui_list_fillBgPen_flat(1)"
dim st3DParamNames[3][2] st3DParamNames[1][1] = "gs_detlevel_3D_m" : st3DParamNames[1][2] = "ui_list_detailLevel3D_flat(1)" st3DParamNames[2][1] = "gs_resol" : st3DParamNames[2][2] = "ui_list_resol_flat(1)" st3DParamNames[3][1] = "gs_shadow" : st3DParamNames[3][2] = "ui_list_shadow_flat(1)"
dim stSurfaceParamNames[1][2] stSurfaceParamNames[1][1] = "gs_molding_mat" : stSurfaceParamNames[1][2] = "ui_list_surface_flat(1)"
file_dependence "ui_list_contLineType_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_contourPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillBgPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_detailLevel3D_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_resol_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_shadow_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_surface_flat(1)"
call "ui_structure_Representation" parameters all bDraw2DGroupList = 1, listfieldID = TABID_REPRES, listFieldPosY = 0, listFieldHeight = 265, stDescHeader = "", stValueHeader = "", st2DParamNames = st2DParamNames, st3DParamNames = st3DParamNames, stSurfaceParamNames = stSurfaceParamNames
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! image list for archive ! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- file_dependence "ui_list_contLineType_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_contourPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillType_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_fillBgPen_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_detailLevel3D_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_resol_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_shadow_flat(1)" file_dependence "ui_list_surface_flat(1)" return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "descriptionPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
dim stParamNames[16] stParamNames[1] = "gs_list_cost" stParamNames[2] = "gs_list_manufacturer" stParamNames[3] = "gs_list_note" stParamNames[4] = "gs_list_location" stParamNames[5] = "gs_list_accessories" stParamNames[6] = "FM_Type" stParamNames[7] = "FM_InventoryNumber" stParamNames[8] = "FM_SerialNumber" stParamNames[9] = "FM_ProductionYear" stParamNames[10] = "FM_ObjectWeight" stParamNames[11] = "FM_ObjectWeightUnit" stParamNames[12] = "gs_list_custom1" stParamNames[13] = "gs_list_custom2" stParamNames[14] = "gs_list_custom3" stParamNames[15] = "gs_list_custom4" stParamNames[16] = "gs_list_custom5"
call "ui_object_listing" parameters all listfieldID = TABID_DESCRIPTIONS, listFieldPosY = 0, listFieldHeight = 265, stDescHeader = "", stValueHeader = "", stParamNames = stParamNames
return
